{"tid":2113516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史係咁話最新一集：「越王勾踐破吳歸，義士還鄉盡錦衣。」","createTime":"2020-07-18T07:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T04:27:32.000Z","uid":238660,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cd28941cab81a84013d85b1f0a1bd0d3b640a058","tid":2113516,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mMIMRTp0RFY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmMIMRTp0RFY&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiT44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=0da1f5e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mMIMRTp0RFY</a><br />\n<br />\n今集歷史係咁話講嘅係「越王勾踐破吳歸，義士還鄉盡錦衣。」摘自李白《越中覽古》，描繪嘅係勾踐戰勝吳國，一雪前恥後嘅盛況。<br />\n<br />\n詩中冇描述嘅係越王臥薪嘗膽、忍辱負重嘅故事，而眾多嘅復國故事背後亦冇唔被欺壓嘅過去。<br />\n<br />\n復國運動中最為人所知係猶太嘅錫安主義，因為猶太人千百年嚟流離於歐洲各國，成為國家不穩時被社會排擠的對象，冠以毒瘤嘅罪名，成為政權嘅代罪羔羊。<br />\n<br />\n對猶太人的迫害最終喺納粹時期，惡化成種族滅絕嘅永久夢魘，幸而二戰後獲得英美支持下成功「復國」，建立以色列。<br />\n<br />\n今集綜觀各地復國之路，睇反殖運動，談復國與竊國之別；但見成功復國者不免踏上壓迫他族的後路，或許最需恢復的，係人類善良的初心。"},{"pid":"b22cb7c9aeef64defd6d04196e0b78793a349592","tid":2113516,"uid":238660,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"ee88ea069051016f5af844b6f82f387291d2aaf6","tid":2113516,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:57:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"250baa49f8efb97826606d63bb8e39a814de9c4a","tid":2113516,"uid":113277,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:59:43.000Z","msg":"呢個名真係好大膽。會唔會繼鏗鏘集之後又被投訴到收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92b12cf3ca5b4974e4ff9f74f96ebaab771959b","tid":2113516,"uid":182822,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"250baa49f8efb97826606d63bb8e39a814de9c4a","tid":2113516,"uid":113277,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:59:4